 541:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****   * @brief Initialize the multiprocessor mode according to the specified
 542:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_uart.c ****   *        parameters in the UART_InitTypeDef and initialize the associated handle.
